{"tid":2198063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"條女俾人非禮仲blame the victim？","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:04:17.000Z","uid":247211,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc41c453b760b1ace7976bfb7c9cf885e1b168b2","tid":2198063,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:30:28.000Z","msg":"昨日（10日）一名水警督察與19歲少女出席一個朋友聚會，消遣過後男方邀請少女返回柴灣翠灣邨寓所。二人其後同乘一輛的士，車程期間男方疑曾親吻及胸襲少女。而少女母親遲遲未見女兒歸家，遂四出打探，終找到男方位於翠灣邨的住所，惟無人應門。少女母親心急如焚，留在翠灣邨一帶守候，豈料卻發現女兒不勝酒力醉倒街頭。事件剛巧亦被巡警發現，該名水警督察涉嫌非禮罪被捕。據了解，被捕男子與少女為中學校友，二人相識約5年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母過左成年幾仲痴埋去隻冇人性既狗度<br />\n冇姦埋你係可惜唔會有人可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">你唔撚係victim呀臭閪</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b851ec6ea4be4e1c1deb70c92a9ca90d96894dd3","tid":2198063,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"勿通匪類就係咁解"},{"pid":"9870b08927b4f5b05029c88fa554de77dce865a3","tid":2198063,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"黑警係黑社會係色魔係變態佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">犯法就係犯法, 除非你係警察, 最後咪又係冇事, 屌</span>"},{"pid":"f7deffc33cd0f7917f29d65202ebe079b2550bb2","tid":2198063,"uid":189799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"條女用個胸襲警，拉得"},{"pid":"fa72b3cf37e305b2ab7025142b6eb943fae9e4e0","tid":2198063,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fa9917d9bc701e632fbed11542adf5238d2f806","tid":2198063,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"拒絕警務人員罪"},{"pid":"b517ef60092ebdc7294c0f2a9a0c3437bd24732c","tid":2198063,"uid":370061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,